@page "/about"
@inject BusinessInfoService InfoService

<h2 class="section-title">About @InfoService.ApplicationName</h2>

<div class="content-section">
    <p>
        Card Factory is a dedicated destination for card game enthusiasts, bringing together a wide collection of classic, 
        modern, and strategy-based card games under one platform.
    </p>
    <p>
        We curate and offer popular games such as UNO, Pokémon cards, and many more—carefully selected to deliver fun, competition, 
        and memorable experiences for players of all ages. Whether you’re a casual player, or a collector seeking iconic decks,
        Card Factory makes discovering the right game simple and enjoyable.
    </p>
    <p>
        At Card Factory, we believe card games are more than just entertainment—they bring people together, spark creativity, 
        and create lasting moments.
    </p>
</div>

